C. Cisco IOS Software

Answer: D
Explanation:
Cisco TrustSec uniquely provides a policy-based platform, the Cisco Identity Services
Engine, that offers integrated posture, profiling and guest services to make context-aware
access control decisions.
Cisco TrustSec uniquely builds upon your existing identity-aware infrastructure by enforcing
these policies in a scalable manner. It also helps to ensure complete data confidentiality
using ubiquitous encryption between network devices.
